Project: Keystone Notary Group, LLC Website
Purpose: High-end, professional notary website for mobile and remote appointments.
Visual style: Minimalist, dark/charcoal/metallic aesthetic, geometric design.
Stack: React, TailwindCSS, Vite (stable versions only)
Project features: SEO metadata, sitemap generation, PWA manifest and icons.
Future plans: Add appointment request with owner confirmation. Video hero animation.

